Remarks.
Stenocrates species
recorded from Peru are
Stenocrates bicarinatus Robinson, 1948
;
Stenocrates carbo Prell, 1937
;
Stenocrates celatus Prell, 1937
;
Stenocrates clipeatus Endrödi 1966
;
Stenocrates cognatus Endrödi, 1966
;
Stenocrates cultor Burmeister, 1847
;
Stenocrates haackae Ratcliffe, 1977
;
S. holomelanus
;
S. lissothorax
;
Stenocrates mimeomus Ratcliffe, 2015
;
Stenocrates minutus Endrödi, 1966
;
Stenocrates nasutus Dechambre, 1979
;
Stenocrates omissus Endrödi, 1966
;
Stenocrates popei Endrödi, 1971
; and
Stenocrates serendipitus Ratcliffe, 2015
.
